abstract: Celebrities, including Lena Dunham and Gwyneth Paltrow, attend fourth annual Hamptons Paddle & Party for Pink fund-raiser, event to benefit Breast Cancer Research Foundation.
lead_paragraph: The actress had a scare on the water at the fourth annual Hamptons Paddle & Party for Pink, which raised money for the Breast Cancer Research Foundation.

headline.main: Lena Dunham Survives to Party in the Hamptons
